and address sanitizer, a heap-buffer overflow occurs when running:
echo 'Ywp2XTCqCi4KeQpAMA==' <pipe> base64 -d > fuzz000.txt
vim -u NONE -X -Z -e -s -S fuzz000.txt -c :qa!

